{
  "stem": "27390.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And this note, somehow, came back with the clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Later on, they found other things and-- and some of the things were from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Money-- ghetto money was found, identification.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We all had identity-- identity cards in the ghetto, so some identity cards from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Some of these-- these clothes was from people that were taken away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So my mother came home that evening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And she was terribly upset.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But she wasn't allowed to tell anybody about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And she told us, but we were not mentioning it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We didn't mention it to anybody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in the beginning, we-- we did not-- we did get-- they started sending in horse meat into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have any-- any kosher meat anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for about a year, I didn't touch it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- I was starving hungry, but I didn't touch it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think my-- my-- my sister did eat it, not right in the beginning but later on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But after about a year, [LAUGHS] we couldn't even get a hold of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they didn't-- they didn't give it to us anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We would have eaten it, but we didn't get it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- and also, and-- and-- and when I started working in this factory, in the tailoring factory, we had to work on the shabbat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We worked six days a week, from-- from about half-past 7:00 or 8:00 in the morning till 6:00 in the evening.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on Sundays, we also worked a half a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was voluntary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we were offered a-- a bowl of soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For working Sunday, we got a-- a bowl of soup, so everybody volunteered to work on Sunday, as well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't have much free time.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
